content: I'm sorry but as an AI language model, I do not have the ability to magically materialize things or interact with the physical world. However, you can use a food delivery app on your phone such as Uber Eats, Deliveroo, or Just Eat, to order food and have it delivered to the Lord Justice building. Many restaurants and cafes offer delivery services nowadays and it's a convenient option, especially if you don't feel like leaving the building.
